response.overview: This event took place on July 20th. 2024 at the Shin-Kiba 1st RING in Tokyo, Japan. Matches featured: • Nagisa Nozaki vs. Komomo Minami • Misa Matsui vs. Bozilla • Utami Hayashishita vs. CHIAKI • Marigold Twin Star Title Tournament First Round Match: Mai Sakurai & MIRAI vs. Myla Grace & Zayda Steel • Nanae Takahashi & Rea Seto vs. Chika Goto & Kouki Amarei • Miku Aono, Natsumi Showzuki & Sareee vs. Giulia, Kizuna Tanaka & Victoria Yuzuki. The event was presented by the Dream Star Fighting Marigold wrestling promotion.
